{"tid":1158202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國右翼政黨NPD選舉廣告遭電視台拒播，但被聯邦憲法法院勒令必須播放","createTime":"2019-05-16T20:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T11:25:18.000Z","uid":41243,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"56739e586e8d1d215fa28d26324aee23e61cf27f","tid":1158202,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T20:28:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.tagesschau.de/inland/wahlwerbespot-npd-101.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tagesschau.de%2Finland%2Fwahlwerbespot-npd-101.html&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEXwmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=a68fcdbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.tagesschau.de/inland/wahlwerbespot-npd-101.html</a><br />\n<br />\n歐洲議會選舉即將舉行，德國被歸類為極右翼政黨德國國家民主黨(NPD)選舉廣告以以下對白開頭：「自2015年邊界被隨意開放、人口無限制擁入德國以來，幾乎每日都有德國人民成為受害者。」隨後廣告播放大量暴力罪案現場及受害者圖片，並提出應該設立「可令德國人民感到安全的保護區」。<br />\n<br />\n柏林-布蘭登堡廣播公司(RBB)拒絕播放NPD的選舉廣告，認為廣告含有明顯嚴重觸犯煽動民眾罪(Volksverhetzung)的內容。NPD提出法律申訴，但於行政法院敗訴，因「廣告將移民普遍歸類為罪犯」。<br />\n<br />\n但聯邦憲法法院則有不同觀點，勒令電視台必須播放廣告。<br />\n<br />\n是否觸犯煽動罪在於影片有否對一部份民眾指責、試圖使之受鄙視或誹謗，以使其尊嚴受侵犯。重點是，廣告本身有否否定一部份民眾的人類尊嚴，與該黨本身的選舉綱領無關。由於廣告中只有邊界開放及人口擁入被指為威脅，因此並無侵犯任何人的尊嚴。<br />\n<br />\n但法庭不允許廣告的最初包含持刀罪犯及血腥內容的版本播出。此一最初版本曾經被公營電視台ZDF拒絕播放。<br />\n<br />\nNPD被允許播出的修剪版本選舉廣告：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nEpqd5rLVpI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnEpqd5rLVpI&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEXwmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=58e18c07\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nEpqd5rLVpI</a>"},{"pid":"124b0f36c5c08bea3f32f039ac624dae3ce223df","tid":1158202,"uid":41243,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T20:34:54.000Z","msg":"曾經聽過一個德國講，佢同一個伊斯蘭移民(唔知係咪難民出身)傾過計，佢都話投NPD <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過都合理既，已經嚟咗就唔想再有更多人嚟分薄資源 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dfaa1457ed82caa6bf1a9d2717af678d0ef2328","tid":1158202,"uid":41243,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T21:01:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cLSEBx0CrtU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcLSEBx0CrtU&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEXwmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=02ddafe2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cLSEBx0CrtU</a><br />\nNPD v.s. AfD<br />\nNPD: AfD哋抄我哋既<br />\nAfD: 梗係唔係，佢哋係極端份子，我哋係支持民主體制既政黨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e730a10f58ab58fb5c0457829fbab6eb58780fc","tid":1158202,"uid":185606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dfaa1457ed82caa6bf1a9d2717af678d0ef2328","tid":1158202,"uid":41243,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T21:01:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cLSEBx0CrtU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcLSEBx0CrtU&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEXwmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=02ddafe2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cLSEBx0CrtU</a><br />\nNPD v.s. AfD<br />\nNPD: AfD哋抄我哋既<br />\nAfD: 梗係唔係，佢哋係極端份子，我哋係支持民主體制既政黨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T21:29:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08c5d1cbe17e8387fe562b42746592f627639813","tid":1158202,"uid":31637,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T23:14:57.000Z","msg":"發現世界各地既左膠已經癲到就快變成另一個共產黨"},{"pid":"3751a332e0f56bb4af89a6f9b589b10190500f8d","tid":1158202,"uid":41243,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"08c5d1cbe17e8387fe562b42746592f627639813","tid":1158202,"uid":31637,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T23:14:57.000Z","msg":"發現世界各地既左膠已經癲到就快變成另一個共產黨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T00:03:30.000Z","msg":"NPD喺1964年成立以嚟都一直面臨畀人取締，因為佢哋被視為新納粹同埋對德國基本法有敵意，只不過因為佢哋勢力太細所以容許佢哋存在，都唔係近期先開始既事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而AfD出現六年，就已經喺Bundestag有議席，成員係NPD幾倍，NPD五十年一個議席都冇，但係其實兩者喺好多議題立場都重疊<br />\nNPD實好葡萄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5dbd3f34a92527633b22adf2ae3c47df079ac4a","tid":1158202,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T01:03:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d160d9f9aefd762d6e2d8029ce53cf6fae8a8c48","tid":1158202,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:57:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bbbcc9ecb3b2ade6d8b258e817e0a3d5c38cb09","tid":1158202,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T11:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b7b468155795ec2203f3be0c17e87c1ad9cc484","tid":1158202,"uid":185606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T11:52:35.000Z","msg":"我記得佢試過俾政府間諜滲透到全國大部分支部都係由間諜做主席"},{"pid":"7f4c24b3d533ff7b0e4b7e9c385f9064980c1e70","tid":1158202,"uid":40216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T11:54:43.000Z","msg":"NPD真係新納粹喎，唔係老屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"678292251f1c2b72a9edc0c3994f23d6c13b1ba0","tid":1158202,"uid":41243,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5b7b468155795ec2203f3be0c17e87c1ad9cc484","tid":1158202,"uid":185606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T11:52:35.000Z","msg":"我記得佢試過俾政府間諜滲透到全國大部分支部都係由間諜做主席"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T11:55:20.000Z","msg":"有冇source <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過印象中希特拉當年都係德國陸軍間碟，受命刺探德國工人黨，點知俾佢做埋主席，改名做國家社會主義德國工人黨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c4ec23cec7358efad2aa